China to Double Spending on ‘Circular Economy,’ Daily Says

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-07-25T23:53:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-25/china-to-double-spending-on-circular-economy-daily-says.html
China will double spending to
promote energy conservation, emission reduction and waste
recycling to 2 billion yuan this year,  China Daily  reported,
citing He Bingguang, an official at the National Development and
Reform Commission.  The commission will use financial support and tax breaks to
encourage investment in the so-called circular economy, the
newspaper cited He as saying.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gregory Turk at 
 gturk2@bloomberg.net  